Description: ======================================
        Scrapy statsd middleware demonstration
        ======================================
        
        Installation
        ============
        
        pip install scrapy-statsd
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
        	DOWNLOADER_MIDDLEWARES = {
        	  'statsd_middleware.StatsdMiddleware': 543,
        	}
        	
        	SPIDER_MIDDLEWARES = {
        	  'statsd_middleware.StatsdMiddleware': 543,
        	}
        
        
        Example Implementation
        ======================
        
        see /example
        install docker
        run it via docker-compose
        see the graphite graph...
